</span></h1><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-185_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-186_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cZMNgc bNHzPH pf-187_"><i class="sc-fbyfCU cFdiHx pf-188_ pfa pfa-book-open-reader" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>Lewis Normoyle</h3><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cZMNgc bNHzPH pf-189_"><i class="sc-fbyfCU cFdiHx pf-190_ pfa pfa-calendar-days" data-pf-type="Icon"></i>07-03-2023</h3></div></div></div><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085713026.png?v=1678085725" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085713026.png?v=1678085725 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085713026_1000x.png?v=1678085725 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085713026_500x.png?v=1678085725 320w" width="4000" height="2667" alt="What is National Careers Week? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="What is National Careers Week? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-191_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-2b32" data-category="Generic Content" data-name="Matcha" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-hAcGzb jHOovW pf-192_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-eGPXGI cIlovf"><div class="sc-iCfMLu eehqFj pf-193_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-XxNYO eWQzGj pf-194_"><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-195_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-197_">In the UK, National Careers Week is celebrated on the second week of March to empower young people to make informed choices about their next steps by ensuring they get the best career advice and information possible.<br><br>Throughout this article, you will learn more about National Careers Week and gain a better understanding of its importance.<br>
</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-198_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-200_">What is National Careers Week?</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085900419.jpg?v=1678085908" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085900419.jpg?v=1678085908 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/what-is-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678085900419_500x.jpg?v=1678085908 320w" width="4000" height="2661" alt="What is National Careers Week? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="What is National Careers Week? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-201_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-202_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-204_">National Careers Week (NCW) is a one-week celebration of career guidance and available resources in education across the UK. It aims to focus on career guidance activities at a crucial time in the academic year to help young people develop the awareness and excitement needed to pursue their future endeavours.<br><br>NCW is a week-long activity for schools, colleges, universities, alternative provision settings, and other organisations to work towards. In addition, educators can utilise digital and video resources to support planning and delivery.<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-205_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-207_">Who founded National Careers Week?
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/who-founded-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678086160254.png?v=1678086175" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/who-founded-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678086160254.png?v=1678086175 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/who-founded-national-careers-week--dr-richard-dune--1678086160254_500x.png?v=1678086175 320w" width="4000" height="2667" alt="Who founded National Careers Week? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Who founded National Careers Week? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-208_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-209_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-211_">The event is founded by a number of volunteers with a combined wealth of experience from the Education, Business and Careers Guidance sectors and is run as a non-profit organisation.<br><br>With evidence showing at the government level that this is an area that needs improvement, National Careers Week aims to improve the level of career education in schools and colleges. Future generations must have access to quality and meaningful interactions that will enable them to understand the connections between courses, skills, and career paths.<br>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-212_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-214_">Why is National Careers Week important?
</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/why-is-national-careers-week-important--dr-richard-dune--1678086457376.png?v=1678086461" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/why-is-national-careers-week-important--dr-richard-dune--1678086457376.png?v=1678086461 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/why-is-national-careers-week-important--dr-richard-dune--1678086457376_500x.png?v=1678086461 320w" width="1250" height="833" alt="Why is National Careers Week important? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Why is National Careers Week important? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-215_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-216_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-218_">National Careers Week provides young people with information about their career options and helps them make informed choices about their future. It highlights the importance of high-quality career education and provides opportunities for children and young people to engage with the world of work.<br>
<br>We are pleased to have you on board to support these initiatives as you determine the right path for your future.
